        Parameterized constructor for a van. Must include the vinNumber, licensePlate, raw company ID, and retail price because no setters exist. The specific Company ID for the van. The van's ID modifier = 02
        Parameters:
        make - The make of the van.
        model - The model of the van.
        year - The year of the van.
        color - The color of the van.
        numberOfCylinders - The number of cylinders in the van's engine.
        numberOfDoors - The number of doors on the van.
        vinNumber - The VIN number of the van.
        licensePlate - The license plate number of the van.
        companyID - The raw company ID for the vehicle.
        dailyRentalPrice - The daily rental price of the vehicle.
